page.title: 11ONE DAY OF MY LIFE
page.content:
I get up in the morning and go to the {bathroom.}When I get out of the bathroom there's usually a big queue out side the bathroom door.I make my breakfast of cornflakes.After breakfast I get my coat on and go to school.When I get to school I play football until the bell goes at 9 o'clock.I play cricket for the school team we have won all the matches so far.After that it is dinner time.Then we go back to our lesson.In that lesson we wrote a story about anything.I wrote a murder story.After the last lesson i had cricket practice.I go to the mosque I read the Karan.I fin ish mosque at half past six'then I come home.Then I have super of chicken or lamb chops.Then I do my home work and go to sleep.
by TARIQ SADDIQUE
